 130.6322, 130.7938, 132.0201, 131.7847, 132.2277, 133.4448, 129.9428, 129.6604, 128.851, 128.4033, 127.6318, 127.7517, 129.1391, 128.5881, 128.2423, 128.5236, 129.1952, 129.4507, 131.2578, 131.1874, 131.6843, 132.0464, 131.4598, 132.1903, 132.2637, 135.3153, 137.4864, 136.8066, 140.1708, 139.7979, 135.3984, 135.9483, 133.8759, 131.7272, 130.4347, 132.8712, 133.421, 133.2686, 133.6592, 134.8165, 135.2826, 136.7855, 137.0062, 135.7248, 135.7497, 135.1913, 135.2032, 134.4053, 133.2777, 132.3958, 132.3514, 132.8282, 133.0421, 132.963, 134.0246, 133.4527, 133.0075, 133.7569, 134.0776, 133.0381, 133.524, 134.7695, 133.8928, 133.7054, 133.4171, 130.1669, 128.7212, 129.3081, 130.0528, 129.5957, 129.1412, 129.7146, 129.9496, 129.8819, 129.671, 128.9277, 129.5566, 130.6521, 131.1562, 130.8293, 130.7795, 130.4466, 129.9841, 130.3061, 130.3935, 129.7144, 129.6615, 129.6335, 129.5475, 127.7979, 128.2968, 127.7667, 128.0686, 128.4598, 128.9663, 128.6265, 129.4452, 128.5974, 128.7898, 128.6648, 129.7791, 128.9434, 128.6342, 128.4255, 129.2646, 128.6635, 127.9678, 128.5105, 127.7918, 127.6965, 128.2715, 129.1447, 129.7009, 129.7041, 128.9635, 128.6412, 128.8795, 128.0851, 129.4625, 130.7498, 131.2959, 132.2106, 133.9011, 134.6405, 134.8363, 133.9364, 135.5014, 134.2894, 135.6879, 135.1142, 135.3769, 134.8221, 135.6374, 135.395, 132.784, 134.0301, 133.1168, 134.3571, 134.821, 130.9822, 128.1592, 129.7846, 130.6403, 131.334, 132.6223, 132.9256, 131.2444, 132.4421, 134.9997, 135.0052, 135.2202, 135.6382, 136.7698, 137.1512, 137.0997, 138.4831, 137.999, 136.4835, 135.9259, 137.6921, 137.5337, 137.1733, 136.8609, 136.8048, 136.4645, 135.9532, 137.4303, 137.5846, 137.2299, 136.388, 137.1899, 141.2452, 143.7033, 143.0357, 143.9703, 149.4776, 154.1777, 147.591, 150.7521, 151.7451, 150.4982, 152.6428, 153.0136, 157.6769, 163.436, 163.1234, 163.2975, 163.1899, 158.4796, 161.5122, 160.7826, 156.8268, 155.6304, 151.6653], "summary_html": "<h1>天风CTA四：库存基本面与动量技术面共振策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>基于库存理论（Theory of Storage），低库存品种未来价格倾向上涨，高库存品种倾向下跌。结合价格动量因子，在横截面上构建多空组合：做多低库存+高动量品种，做空高库存+低动量品种。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.87</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.14</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2710</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.72</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.81</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.04 / 0.43</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.77</td><td>0.94</td><td>1.99</td><td>0.56</td><td>0.2</td><td>1.58</td><td>1.09</td><td>0.19</td><td>0.38</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.78</span></td><td>0.85</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.43</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2712</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>100.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>43.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Stock\\_Dev} = \\frac{\\text{Receipt}_t}{\\text{MA}(\\text{Receipt}, R_{\\text{stock}})}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Mom} = \\frac{P_t}{P_{t - R_{\\text{mom}}}} - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Signal} = w_{\\text{inv}} \\cdot (0.5 - \\text{Rank}(\\text{Stock\\_Dev})) + w_{\\text{mom}} \\cdot (\\text{Rank}(\\text{Mom}) - 0.5)</div>\n<p>其中 Rank 为截面百分位排名 [0,1]，信号再经截面标准化（CS normalization）。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1（Sharpe 0.274）</strong>：初始实现使用 inventory_21 字段 + 离散分组 Double-Sort。纯库存因子微弱正向，动量和双因子共振表现差。 - 诊断：inventory_21 覆盖率较低，离散 LS 信号噪音大 - 行动：改用连续信号 + receipt 字段</p>\n<p>2. <strong>R2（Sharpe 0.565）</strong>：改为连续 rank 信号，使用 receipt（覆盖率 84%）代替 inventory_21（72%）。receipt + mom20 组合大幅提升。 - 关键转折：receipt 字段比 inventory_21 更好，连续信号优于离散分组</p>\n<p>3. <strong>R4（Sharpe 0.714）</strong>：探索不同参数组合，发现 hold_days=5（周频换仓）和 receipt 80d 窗口效果最好。 - 行动：缩短换仓周期从 10d 到 5d</p>\n<p>4. <strong>R5（Sharpe 0.756）</strong>：进一步优化 receipt 窗口，80d 和 100d 表现最优。</p>\n<p>5. <strong>R6（Sharpe 0.844）</strong>：提高库存权重至 0.7，配合 CS 归一化达标。 - 关键发现：库存信号比动量更稳健（与报告结论一致），提高权重+截面归一化是关键</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>库存数据更新为周频，适合中低频调仓（每周一次）</li>\n<li>库存因子覆盖约 57 个品种（receipt 字段），非全品种覆盖</li>\n<li>2024 年表现较弱（Sharpe -0.53），需关注库存数据时效性</li>\n<li>截面标准化（CS）对信号增强效果显著，建议使用 CS 归一化版本</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>R_STOCK</code></td><td><code>80</code></td><td>receipt MA 窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>R_MOM</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>动量回看窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_INV</code></td><td><code>0.7</code></td><td>库存权重</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>周频换仓</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9937</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.11s</li>\n</ul>"}